  "disclaimer": "Control-review evidence only; not a compliance determination, launch approval, or attestation. No finding has been closed and no filing or system-of-record change has been made.",
  "narrative": "Control review of the USDX Payment Stablecoin program for the period ending 2026-07-15 evaluated 18 controls across reserve, custody, screening, transaction, operational, reconciliation, and disclosure categories. Two findings were identified. Reserve backing is under 1:1 (backing ratio 0.9980 against a 1.0 minimum), a critical-control deficiency evidenced by the June reserve attestation. Chain reorg/fork handling is not evidenced, an operational gap. All other evaluated controls are supported by cited evidence. Because a critical reserve control is deficient, the suggested review disposition is Material Gaps - Escalate: route the findings to the accountable control owners and compliance for human adjudication and remediation planning. This review evidences findings and recommends next steps; it does not decide, adjudicate, or record any outcome. Control-review evidence only; not a compliance determination, launch approval, or attestation. No finding has been closed and no filing or system-of-record change has been made."
